lead_paragraph: Jeff Green scored 16 points, including two free throws with 6.2 seconds left, to help the Memphis Grizzlies hold off the New York Knicks 91-85 on Friday night for their fifth straight win.

headline.print_headline: Green Scores 16 Points and Grizzlies Hold Off Knicks 91-85
